data.title: Martell Webster Wants to Intern for Singer Ryan Leslie
data.meta_description: Internships are all the rage for NBA dudes this summer, but unlike Brandon Jennings, Martell Webster is looking to intern for another entertainer instead
data.text: Internships are all the rage for NBA dudes this summer, but unlike Brandon Jennings, Martell Webster is looking to intern for another entertainer instead of a company. From his Twitter page (via BDL): “@ryanleslie hey man my name is martell webster. I know your boy Shiv. NBA has a lockout and I would love to get mentorship under you bro. I mean that on the most loving and humble level.”
